# 07 - Recipe Creator
# Generate recipes based on ingredients

NAME recipe-creator
INPUT ingredients
INPUT cuisine DEFAULT "any"
INPUT dietary DEFAULT "none"

GOAL brainstorm "Given these ingredients: $ingredients, brainstorm 3 possible $cuisine dishes. Consider $dietary dietary restrictions."
GOAL select "Choose the best recipe based on: ingredient usage, flavor balance, and preparation simplicity."
GOAL detail "Write the complete recipe with: ingredients list, step-by-step instructions, timing, and tips."

RUN create USING brainstorm, select, detail
